sentences.sentence: The coma duration prognostication model can prognosticate the duration of coma.
sentences.translation: 结论：昏迷时间预测模型可为临床提供昏迷时间预测。

sentences.sentence: Unfortunately, I am not able to prognosticate how everything will eventually shake out.
sentences.translation: 不幸的是，我无法预言每件事的最终结果将会怎样。

sentences.sentence: Results emphasize the importance of the family history when trying to prognosticate in an individual case.
sentences.translation: 结果强调家庭的重要性历史当试图预言在个别案件。
